		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="408" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「声援」聚集冰元素之力，随后迸发，扣除前台角色<span color="#ffccbf">60%</span><span>生命值</span><span color="#ff9999">(无法躲避)</span><span>，可致死。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「声援」朝玩家方向蓄力，间断迸发5次寒涛冽流，造成<span color="#99ffff">70%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1411" y="511" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「声援」在玩家处召唤白晶流幕，持续造成<span color="#99ffff">20%,10%,5%,2%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="442" height="229" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「声援」在场地上分显「佑灵身」，为友方单位，初始仅有10%生命值。<br/>当队伍中任意角色恢复生命值时，「佑灵身」也将恢复等量生命值。<br/>「佑灵身」死亡时，会对「声援」造成基于其攻击力<span color="#99ffff">300%</span><span>的伤害。<br/>「佑灵身」存在22s，再次生成「佑灵身」则需等待至少40s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="422" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「声援」凝聚碎冰，片刻后向前扇形区域挥洒暴风雪，持续造成<span color="#99ffff">50%,25%,<br/>12.5%,5%</span><span>伤害</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
